thread.title: Jillian

author: Jillian
title: Jillian
text: I was eager to buy these as they came recommended by friends. I was a little surprised with the size but that may have been my fault as I didn't see the size of the stickers on the ordering site. They were larger than expected as I my friends labels for cups/plates etc were much smaller. I only recall having one option for clicking though. Either way, they look great and the delivery was very fast!
